  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Fetching messages still flashes when you have a contact request in the mailbox. It's because it fetches again the messages for the particular topic that gets added.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nFetching messages status should not be repeated when there is a contact request in chat list. It should not distract a user.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nFetching messages still flashes when you have a contact request in the mailbox.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status on 2 devices\r\n- Device 1: Add device 2\r\n- Device 2: Do not accept the contact \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, May 24\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
